meta {
  name: Retrieve a JSON Web Key Set (JWKS) for the default provisioning connection
  type: http
  seq: 3
}

get {
  url: {{orgUrl}}/api/v1/apps/{{appId}}/connections/default/jwks
  body: none
  auth: none
}

headers {
  Accept: application/json
  Authorization: SSWS {{apiKey}}
}

docs {
Retrieves a JWKS for the default provisioning connection.  This can be used by the OAuth 2.0 app's `jwk_uri` property in the target org.

**Responses:**
- `200`: OK
- `401`: 
- `404`: 
- `429`:
}
